data.text: Let me tell y’all something, stop acting like the victim here and start growing up, you ranting like this all day won’t get you anywhere, accept the reality bruh, if you hate people callig you immature why not changing your own attitude first.

Trending the #endviolence ? Trying to end all bullying when y’all are the one who started shits and fanwars mentioning EXO everywhere you go. What’s the point of you trending that? Hypocrites, just for the ‘good’ face am I right?

Armys have seriously gone too far this time. Is this how your parents taught you to be respectful? Don’t give your favs the bad image cuz “fans are the face of idols” the Kings and Queens of pop song didn’t work hard for you to say shits like that to them.
